data.title: List of Graduates
data.text:
This page holds the list of undergraduate students who have applied on time for December 2023 and Winter 23/24 graduation by college. These graduation lists are posted for Spring/May and Winter/December Commencement and are not updated with late applicants.

Important Note: In order for this honors distinction to be noted, students must have earned a qualifying cumulative GPA by the semester prior to commencement.

Latin Honors

Students who have earned Latin honors are noted by the asterisk next to their name:

* Cum Laude: Cumulative GPA 3.250-3.499

** Magna Cum Laude: Cumulative GPA 3.500-3.749

*** Summa Cum Laude: Cumulative GPA 3.750-4.000

This list does not guarantee degree conferral as final grades are not posted when this list is generated. The lists below are not updated with late applicants.
